==English==

===Verb===
{{en-verb|suffic|ing}}

# To be enough, or [[sufficient]]; to meet the [[need]] (of anything); to be equal to the end proposed; to be adequate.
# To satisfy; to content; to be equal to the wants or demands of.
# To furnish; to supply adequately.

